'''阿鲁语'''是一种在[[中国|中国]][[云南省|云南省]][[金平苗族瑶族傣族自治县|金平苗族瑶族傣族自治县]]、[[绿春县|绿春县]]、[[江城哈尼族彝族自治县|江城哈尼族彝族自治县]]和[[元阳县|元阳县]]使用的未被分类的[[彝语|彝语]]。阿鲁人也被外族人称为鲁乌或倮乌。<ref name="wanmin">{{cite web|url=http://www.wanmin.org/minzu/alu|title=阿鲁民族 - 万民网|website=wanmin.org|access-date=2017-12-30|archive-date=2021-01-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210116034427/http://www.wanmin.org/minzu/alu|dead-url=no}}</ref>中国之外也有500至600名阿鲁人生活在[[老挝|老挝]][[丰沙里省|丰沙里省]]本代县。<ref>Schliesinger, Joachim. 2003. Ethnic Groups of Laos. Vol. 4: Sino-Tibetan-Speaking Peoples. Bangkok: White Lotus Press.</ref>

阿鲁人会在"阿卑节"("少女节")上演奏有5个管的口风琴。<ref name="彝学研究">{{cite web|url=http://www.yixueyanjiu.com/news/13/z_13_24201.html|website=yixueyanjiu.com|title=红河金平"姑娘节" 彝族阿鲁人的情人节_彝学研究网|access-date=2017-12-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171222051241/http://www.yixueyanjiu.com/news/13/z_13_24201.html|archive-date=2017-12-22|dead-url=yes}}</ref>

==分类==
Hsiu (2017)<ref>Hsiu, Andrew. 2017. ''[https://www.academia.edu/35542553/The_Lawu_languages_footprints_along_the_Red_River_valley_corridor The Lawu languages: footprints along the Red River valley corridor] {{Wayback|url=https://www.academia.edu/35542553/The_Lawu_languages_footprints_along_the_Red_River_valley_corridor |date=20191019071012 }}''. {{doi|10.5281/zenodo.1249178}}</ref>认为阿鲁语可能和[[腊罗语|腊罗语]]有亲缘关系，但这因为资料短缺而没有证据支持。

